{"tid":2140011,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【警方對蘋果日報及林卓廷再次誤導市民深感憤慨】","createTime":"2020-08-04T16:14:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-05T03:06:06.000Z","uid":240362,"like":3,"dislike":38,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"8a7aaaa8cd15c392e14b4b9340617e333fc792d3","tid":2140011,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T16:14:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent-hkt1-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/s960x960/116420313_3400465003374773_3576763298802135704_o.jpg?_nc_cat=1&amp;_nc_sid=8024bb&amp;_nc_ohc=SjdCJv1D2IsAX-JYtgM&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkt1-1.xx&amp;_nc_tp=7&amp;oh=1a2b129a9031710d29bd218476e956c7&amp;oe=5F505CB6\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkt1-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2Fs960x960%2F116420313_3400465003374773_3576763298802135704_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D1%26_nc_sid%3D8024bb%26_nc_ohc%3DSjdCJv1D2IsAX-JYtgM%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-hkt1-1.xx%26_nc_tp%3D7%26oh%3D1a2b129a9031710d29bd218476e956c7%26oe%3D5F505CB6&h=db6ca6c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-hkt1-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/s960x960/117190948_3400465116708095_101562048603317117_o.jpg?_nc_cat=1&amp;_nc_sid=8024bb&amp;_nc_ohc=MwbVEIPBa0gAX_K6vMD&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkt1-1.xx&amp;_nc_tp=7&amp;oh=fdaec0df6022d3d8a5e591c4a2a6827f&amp;oe=5F4E4468\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkt1-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2Fs960x960%2F117190948_3400465116708095_101562048603317117_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D1%26_nc_sid%3D8024bb%26_nc_ohc%3DMwbVEIPBa0gAX_K6vMD%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-hkt1-1.xx%26_nc_tp%3D7%26oh%3Dfdaec0df6022d3d8a5e591c4a2a6827f%26oe%3D5F4E4468&h=509c1076&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n警方留意到蘋果日報今日﹙八月四日）有關警察褔利基金的報道。報道抹黑警方「鬼祟」修訂《警察通例》以放寛基金批核程序；並以失實標題，企圖誤導市民警察福利基金收入來源由徵稅所得；更就基金捐款人的身分大造文章。警方感到非常憤慨。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，警方於七月三十一日回覆蘋果日報查詢時，已經明確指出，相關《警察通例》的修訂，是去年根據政府物流服務署的《物料供應及採購規例》所訂明的採購限額而作出，旨在更新已過時的資料，及優化採購程序。修訂工作乃按既定機制進行。<br />\n<br />\n至於警察福利基金的收入來源，詳情均列於《警察福利基金年報》內，年報清楚顯示收入來源並非徵稅所得。<br />\n<br />\n此外，報道又對基金捐款者身分作揣測，更引述了立法會議員林卓廷，指「捐款人亦不乏身分敏感者」。事實上，警察福利基金除了須按相關法例管理外，在接受捐款方面亦須符合公務員事務局有關員工福利基金接受捐款的準則和規定，當中包括捐款不會引起利益衝突和不會惹人誤解，接受捐款的部門不得與捐款人有任何公事往來，捐款不得與個別公務員有關連等。基於尊重捐款人的個人意願，基金管理委員會未能公開披露每個捐款人的資料。<br />\n<br />\n對於蘋果日報及立法會議員林卓廷失實的指控，企圖誤導讀者，居心叵測，警方深感憤怒。"},{"pid":"f3cd7cad851c25a95290240c5b1e9e0fb564680f","tid":2140011,"uid":66221,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T16:24:53.000Z","msg":"閱，不值一提"},{"pid":"f539cffad455c37222b04f0c78c41a29e3f86e41","tid":2140011,"uid":304769,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"8a7aaaa8cd15c392e14b4b9340617e333fc792d3","tid":2140011,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T16:14:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent-hkt1-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/s960x960/116420313_3400465003374773_3576763298802135704_o.jpg?_nc_cat=1&amp;_nc_sid=8024bb&amp;_nc_ohc=SjdCJv1D2IsAX-JYtgM&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkt1-1.xx&amp;_nc_tp=7&amp;oh=1a2b129a9031710d29bd218476e956c7&amp;oe=5F505CB6\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkt1-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2Fs960x960%2F116420313_3400465003374773_3576763298802135704_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D1%26_nc_sid%3D8024bb%26_nc_ohc%3DSjdCJv1D2IsAX-JYtgM%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-hkt1-1.xx%26_nc_tp%3D7%26oh%3D1a2b129a9031710d29bd218476e956c7%26oe%3D5F505CB6&h=db6ca6c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-hkt1-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/s960x960/117190948_3400465116708095_101562048603317117_o.jpg?_nc_cat=1&amp;_nc_sid=8024bb&amp;_nc_ohc=MwbVEIPBa0gAX_K6vMD&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkt1-1.xx&amp;_nc_tp=7&amp;oh=fdaec0df6022d3d8a5e591c4a2a6827f&amp;oe=5F4E4468\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkt1-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2Fs960x960%2F117190948_3400465116708095_101562048603317117_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D1%26_nc_sid%3D8024bb%26_nc_ohc%3DMwbVEIPBa0gAX_K6vMD%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-hkt1-1.xx%26_nc_tp%3D7%26oh%3Dfdaec0df6022d3d8a5e591c4a2a6827f%26oe%3D5F4E4468&h=509c1076&s={SIZE}\" /